Metadata: Coastal Clips (Number 48, 49, and 50, Spring, Summer, and Winter 2019)
Three newsletter issues in one entry for 2019

Coastal Clips i​s a quarterly publication of the Louisiana S​ea Grant Colleg​e Program at Louisiana St​ate University, Baton Rouge, LA. The following main titles are in these issues: Number 48: -​-​ -​ -​ -​-​Tell-​Tail Signs of Louisiana Crawfish; Number 49: HB335 Requires Restaurants to Tell Patrons They’re Eating Imported Seafood; Number 50: Louisiana Fisheries Forward Summit 2020.
